1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,169
Several years ago, while checking student examination papers, I came across one that especially disturbed me.

2
00:00:07,440 --> 00:00:17,409
The student who wrote the examination had demonstrated in class discussions and previous tests that he was far better qualified than his paper indicated.

3
00:00:17,680 --> 00:00:22,690
He was, in fact, the fellow who I thought would finish at the top of the class.

4
00:00:22,880 --> 00:00:25,730
Instead, his paper put him at the bottom.

5
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:34,290
As was my custom in such cases, I had my secretary call the student and ask him to come by my office on an urgent matter.

6
00:00:34,720 --> 00:00:37,090
Paul W. appeared shortly.

7
00:00:37,200 --> 00:00:40,450
He looked as though he had been through a terrible experience.

8
00:00:40,720 --> 00:00:45,330
After he was comfortably seated, I said to him, What happened, Paul?

9
00:00:45,520 --> 00:00:49,649
This just isn't the quality paper I expected you to write.

10
00:00:50,320 --> 00:00:54,849
Paul struggled with himself, looked in the direction of his feet, and replied,

11
00:00:55,359 --> 00:01:00,770
Sir, after I saw that you had spotted me cheating, I just went to pieces.

12
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:03,010
I couldn't concentrate on anything.

13
00:01:03,359 --> 00:01:07,409
Honest, this is the first time I've ever cheated at the university.

14
00:01:07,599 --> 00:01:12,450
I desperately wanted an A, so I worked up a little pony to use.

15
00:01:13,040 --> 00:01:14,930
He was terribly upset.

16
00:01:14,960 --> 00:01:17,810
But now that he was talking, he wouldn't stop.

17
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:21,409
I suppose you'll have to recommend me for dismissal.

18
00:01:21,520 --> 00:01:28,450
The university rule says any student found cheating in any manner is subject to permanent dismissal.

19
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:33,889
Here Paul started bringing up the shame this incident would bring to his family,

20
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:37,570
how it would wreck his life, and all sorts of repercussions.

21
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:40,369
Finally, I said, hold it now.

22
00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:41,730
Slow down.

23
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:43,490
Let me explain something.

24
00:01:43,840 --> 00:01:45,649
I didn't see you cheat.

25
00:01:45,760 --> 00:01:51,090
Until you walked in and told me, I hadn't the faintest idea that was the trouble.

26
00:01:51,359 --> 00:01:53,810
I am sorry, Paul, that you did.

27
00:01:54,320 --> 00:02:01,490
Then I continued, Paul, tell me, just what do you want to gain from your university experience?

28
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:05,730
He was a little calmer now, and after a short pause he said,

29
00:02:06,080 --> 00:02:10,770
well, doctor, I think my overall aim is to learn how to live,

30
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:13,570
but I guess I'm failing pretty badly.

